Rifts Spells
============

Syntax:
  cast <spellname> [at <target>]

Casting costs PPE (Potential Psychic Energy). You must know the spell and
have enough PPE. In combat, casting uses one attack that melee round.

Which spells you know depends on your O.C.C. and race. Type psionics for
psychic powers (separate from magic).

Level 1
-------
  cloud of smoke      Obscuring smoke. All combat rolls -2 strike.
  blinding flash      Blinds target 1d4 rounds. Save vs magic negates.
  levitation          Caster floats. Cannot be tripped or knocked down.
  magic net           Entangles target. Save vs magic (14+) negates.

Level 2
-------
  fire ball           4d6 MDC fire damage. No save.
  carpet of adhesion  Sticky floor. Save vs magic or stuck. -2 APM while trapped.
  invisibility simple Caster invisible. Broken by combat or loud action.

Level 3
-------
  tongues             Target understands all languages for 5 min per level.
  fire bolt           5d6 MDC fire damage.
  armor of ithan      30 MDC magical field for 5 minutes.
  circle of flame     Ring of fire. 2d6 MDC per round to anyone entering.
  telekinesis         Move objects with mind. Lift PS 20 equivalent. 2 minutes.

Level 4
-------
  energy field        100 MDC force barrier for 2 minutes.
  ignite fire         Ignite flammable material within 60 feet.
  multiple image      1d4+1 illusory duplicates for 4 minutes.
  shadow meld         Merge with shadows. Near-invisible for 2 minutes.
  mask of deceit      Appear as a specific person for 10 minutes.

Level 5
-------
  domination          Control one target for 1 minute. Save 16 ME negates.
  escape              Teleport 60 feet to an adjacent area.
  fly                 Fly at 50 mph for 5 minutes.
  horrific illusion   Terrifying vision. Save 14 ME or flee in panic.
  impervious to energy Immune to energy attacks for 2 minutes.
  metamorphosis animal Transform into an animal up to twice your size for 10 minutes.

See also: help cast, score, rest
